    rownames(DEGes) <- DEGes$rownames
    drop.cols <-colnames(DEGes[,grep("padj|pval|rownames", colnames(DEGes))])
    DEGes <- DEGes %>% select(-one_of(drop.cols))
    DEGes <- as.matrix(DEGes)

    paletteLength <- 30
